						               													<description>Note: Not to be confused with Monopoly: Here and Now &amp;#226;&amp;#128;&amp;#147; The World Edition from 2008.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the world&amp;rsquo;s favorite cities in this Here &amp;amp; Now version of the fast-trading property game, Monopoly! The jet-set gameplay will be epic as you race around the world to visit the world&amp;rsquo;s most exciting places and buy locations. Every time you add another stamp to your passport, you get closer to the globetrotting win!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Travel around the gameboard visiting The World's most exciting places.&amp;#10;Pay for the stamps of the places you land on and put them in your passport.&amp;#10;Charge other players vistor fees to stop at places you have stamps for.&amp;#10;The first player to fill their passport wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Different than traditional Monopoly (even previous &amp;quot;Here &amp;amp; Now&amp;quot; Editions) - there are no houses, hotels, or even title deeds. The goal isn't to bankrupt other players (in fact, the rules say if you are out of money, just don't pay - but keep playing). The goal of each player is to fill their own &amp;quot;Passport&amp;quot;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game plays far more like Monopoly Empire than regular Monopoly.&amp;#10;An edition with places in the USA exclusively, also exists: Monopoly: Here &amp;amp; Now (America has voted - powered by BuzzFeed).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
